{"tid":2036431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★mpf 5月又輸！年內累蝕逾兩萬","createTime":"2020-05-26T12:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T15:14:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6aba71b98a52d8146141bd45d8f9b4523539d448","tid":2036431,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:45:24.000Z","msg":"據晨星(亞洲)截至上周五(5月22日)數據，打工仔本月強積金平均蝕0.51%，首5個月則跌7.19%，即打工仔平均仍蝕逾兩萬多元。基金界直指，未來環球股市依然會相當波動，對強積金全年表現不太樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【香港股票蝕得最甘】</strong></span><br />\n據晨星(亞洲)資料顯示，5月份表現最差為香港股票基金類別，錄得5.01%的跌幅；中國及大中華股票跟隨其後，跌2.48%；而亞太區股票(不包括日本)及亞洲股票(不包括日本)則分別跌1.55%及1.27%。至於首5個月計，則仍有6個類別錄得雙位數跌幅，尤以歐洲股票跌近20%最差，而環球股票及日本股票亦錄逾12%跌幅。亞太區股票(不包括日本)期內亦大跌逾17%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200526/bkn-20200526191846067-0526_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200526%2Fbkn-20200526191846067-0526_00842_001.html&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=de918e0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200526/bkn-20200526191846067-0526_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8888ee2d62257869c96cd9ebfc3a8c20f50f95e2","tid":2036431,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:45:49.000Z","msg":"北美<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df68291ea6ddd1ad4ff7299109e9dd5b863a1ac8","tid":2036431,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:45:59.000Z","msg":"老综又贏"},{"pid":"df6f6ac6a9e880821508bac7609fa2e278d76a76","tid":2036431,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:46:43.000Z","msg":"mpf死嗰日都未必拎到<br />\n老虎蟹都買美股"},{"pid":"71291cc87fbcf7c6b8f34581dbdec34e1e409db5","tid":2036431,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:51:48.000Z","msg":"無得拎，驚咩。"},{"pid":"e55a51297cd27b12e51cfc6ac